    @CreoleResource(name="ANNIE VP Chunker",
                comment="ANNIE VP Chunker component.",
                helpURL="http://gate.ac.uk/userguide/sec:parsers:vgchunker",
                icon="pr")
public class VPChunker
extends Transducer
    ANNIE VP Chunker module. It is actually a JAPE grammar; this class is here so we can have a separate entry in creol.xml in order to point to the default VP chunking grammar.
